Package: CoreExplore
Type: Package
Title: Explore Microbiome Core Taxa by Prevalence
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Nick",
                  family = "Pinkham",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "nickvpinkham@gmail.com")
Description: Tools for exploring the core microbiome of a community-by-feature
    count table. The main function bins taxa by how prevalent they are across
    samples (0-10%, 10-20%, ... of samples) and summarises their mean relative
    abundance within each prevalence bin as a stacked bar plot, optionally
    aggregating features to a supplied taxonomic level first.
